name: Synesthesia - Interactive NFT Canary
description:
Synesthesia is a simple interactive NFT created to enable owners to test whether various sites in the Tezos ecosystem support interactive art. Once you acquire the piece, you can try to view it on other ecosystem websites to help you determine whether those sites support the properly display and interactivity available through p5.js.

Instructions: Move the mouse around and click/tap to create colorful pattern. Visit other Tezos ecosystem websites and dApps and try to view it there. If they don't support the format, consider reaching out to them to request support!
